code if you need it, but it shouldn’t matter because the issue persists when using rev hardware client.

I think MAXMotion changed how their PID controller works, so you might need to retune the PID values. (I’m also not versed at all in software so I could be completely wrong!)

I’d also check to make sure that the encoders are sending the correct signals.
